<h2 id='sub-1-2' class='sec-h2'><span>1.2 Initial Business Needs</span> <em class='brass'>(User Brief)</em></h2>
<p>The following needs were submitted in the original brief and triggered Sophie's requirements extraction.</p>
<table class='tbl'>
<thead><tr>
<th><strong>#</strong></th>
<th><strong>Need</strong></th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>1</td>
<td>Inventaire véhicules (marque, modèle, immatriculation, kilométrage, état)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2</td>
<td>Contrats de location (client, véhicule, durée, tarif mensuel)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3</td>
<td>Suivi des maintenances (vidanges, contrôles techniques, réparations)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4</td>
<td>Alertes automatiques : CT à renouveler, entretien prévu, fin de contrat</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>5</td>
<td>Gestion des sinistres et assurances</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6</td>
<td>Facturation mensuelle automatique</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>7</td>
