<section id='sec-2' class='block'>
<div class='act'><span class='act-num'>— Scene II</span><span class='act-sep'></span><span class='act-tag'>Artifact 02</span></div><h1 class='sec-h1'><span>Business Requirements</span> <em class='brass'>(Sophie — PM)</em></h1>
<p>Vehicle fleet management system for a rental company. The project covers vehicle inventory tracking, rental contracts, maintenance scheduling, automated alerts, claims and insurance management, automated monthly billing, and a mobile application for drivers to report issues and submit mileage readings.</p>
<h2 id='sub-2-1' class='sec-h2'><span>2.1 Requirements Summary</span> <em class='brass'>(25 BRs)</em></h2>
<p>All requirements extracted by Sophie, with category, priority, stakeholder, and traceability to use cases.</p>
