<dt>Validation Rules</dt><dd>• Registration must be unique <span class='dot'>·</span> Mileage must be &gt;= 0 <span class='dot'>·</span> Condition must be a defined status value</dd>
<dt>Acceptance Criteria</dt><dd>• User can create a vehicle record with all required fields <span class='dot'>·</span> User can update vehicle information <span class='dot'>·</span> System prevents duplicate registration numbers <span class='dot'>·</span> User can view the full vehicle inventory</dd>
</dl></div></td></tr>
