<dt>Validation Rules</dt><dd>• A contract must reference an existing client and an existing vehicle <span class='dot'>·</span> Start date must be before end date <span class='dot'>·</span> Monthly rate must be &gt; 0 <span class='dot'>·</span> A vehicle can only have one active contract at a time</dd>
<dt>Dependencies</dt><dd>BR-001, BR-005</dd>
<dt>Acceptance Criteria</dt><dd>• User can create a rental contract with all required fields <span class='dot'>·</span> System prevents assigning a vehicle already under active contract <span class='dot'>·</span> User can view all active and past contracts</dd>
