<dt>Main Flow</dt><dd>• Actor navigates to the Vehicle__c list view to browse the fleet inventory. <span class='dot'>·</span> Actor selects a vehicle record to view its details. <span class='dot'>·</span> Actor clicks 'Edit' to modify one or more attributes (e.g., Mileage__c). <span class='dot'>·</span> Actor updates the relevant field values. <span class='dot'>·</span> Actor clicks 'Save' and the record is updated with the new values.</dd>
