<dt>Main Flow</dt><dd>• 1. User navigates to the Rental_Contract__c object and clicks 'New'. <span class='dot'>·</span> 2. User selects the Client (Account lookup) associated with the contract. <span class='dot'>·</span> 3. User selects the Vehicle (Vehicle__c lookup) to be rented. <span class='dot'>·</span> 4. User enters the Start_Datec and End_Datec for the rental period. <span class='dot'>·</span> 5. User enters the Monthly_Rate__c for the contract. <span class='dot'>·</span> 6. User clicks 'Save' and the system creates the Rental_Contract__c record.</dd>
</dl></div>
<div class='uc-card'>
