<h2 id='sub-10-7' class='sec-h2'><span>10.7 Training Risks</span></h2>
<table class='tbl'>
<thead><tr>
<th><strong>Risk</strong></th>
<th><strong>Severity</strong></th>
<th><strong>Mitigation</strong></th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Low driver adoption of mobile app due to tech literacy barriers (150+ drivers, varying tech skills)</td>
<td><strong>high</strong></td>
<td>Simplify mobile app UI to essential features only (problemReportForm and mileageReadingForm LWC), provide in-person demos at driver meetings, create 2-minute video tutorials in multiple languages, assign driver champion for peer support, offer phone-based support hotline</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Resistance from Maintenance Coordinators to new digital workflow (currently paper-based)</td>
<td><strong>medium</strong></td>
<td>Involve Maintenance Coordinators in pilot training, demonstrate time savings from maintenanceCompletionFlow auto-updates, provide side-by-side comparison of old vs. new process, assign dedicated trainer for first 2 weeks post-go-live</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Complexity of rentalContractCreator LWC overwhelming Sales Representatives</td>
<td><strong>medium</strong></td>
<td>Provide extra hands-on practice sessions for M03, create step-by-step job aid with screenshots, record screen-share video of contract creation process, offer 1-on-1 coaching sessions during first week</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Insufficient training time for 150+ drivers (scheduling conflicts, shift work)</td>
<td><strong>high</strong></td>
<td>Offer multiple training session times (morning, afternoon, evening), provide self-paced video option for drivers who cannot attend live sessions, extend training period to 2 weeks if needed, use SMS reminders for session attendance</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Flow failures during training due to sandbox data issues or configuration drift</td>
<td><strong>medium</strong></td>
<td>Refresh training sandbox weekly, validate all 8 flows before each training session, have System Administrator on standby during training, maintain backup sandbox for failover</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Language barriers for drivers (multilingual workforce)</td>
<td><strong>medium</strong></td>
<td>Translate mobile app quick start guide and video tutorials into primary languages (French + 1-2 others based on driver demographics), provide multilingual support hotline, use visual aids and screenshots to minimize text</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>GDPR compliance gaps due to insufficient administrator training on data retention and consent</td>
<td><strong>high</strong></td>
<td>Dedicate 1 hour of M11 specifically to GDPR requirements, provide detailed checklist for data retention policy configuration, conduct quarterly compliance audits, assign GDPR compliance officer role</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Post-go-live support overwhelmed by volume of questions (165+ users going live simultaneously)</td>
<td><strong>high</strong></td>
<td>Staff 2 support personnel during first week (1 for internal users, 1 for drivers), leverage champions for tier-1 support, create comprehensive FAQ based on pilot feedback, use Chatter for self-service Q&amp;A, extend office hours to 10 hours/day for first week</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</section>
