<h2 id='sub-12-4' class='sec-h2'><span>12.4 CI/CD Pipeline</span></h2>
<table class='tbl'>
<thead><tr>
<th>Tool</th>
<th>GitHub Actions + Salesforce CLI (sf)</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Branching strategy</td>
<td>model: GitFlow branches: {"main":"Production-ready code, deployed to PROD after UAT sign-off","develop":"Integration branch for sprint work, auto-deployed to QA sandbox","feature/<em>":"Individual features (e.g., feature/mobile-problem-report), deployed to DEV sandboxes","release/</em>":"Release candidates (e.g., release/v1.0), deployed to UAT for stakeholder validation","hotfix/*":"Emergency fixes (e.g., hotfix/invoice-calculation-bug), merged to main + develop"}</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 class='sec-h3'>Workflows</h3>
<table class='tbl'>
<thead><tr>
<th><strong>Workflow</strong></th>
<th><strong>Description / triggers</strong></th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>validate-pr</strong></td>
<td class='td-json'><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Checkout code</span> <span class='chip'>Authenticate to QA sandbox using SFDX auth URL</span> <span class='chip'>Run PMD static analysis (sf scanner run --target 'force-app/**/*.cls' --format table)</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy metadata with --check-only flag (sf project deploy start --check-only --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Run all Apex tests, verify 85%+ coverage</span> <span class='chip'>Report code coverage and PMD violations as PR comment</span> <span class='chip'>Block merge if tests fail or coverage &lt; 85%</span></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>deploy-qa</strong></td>
<td class='td-json'><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Checkout develop branch</span> <span class='chip'>Authenticate to QA sandbox</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy metadata (sf project deploy start --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Run all Apex tests</span> <span class='chip'>Execute post-deployment smoke tests (verify key flows execute)</span> <span class='chip'>Notify team via Slack webhook with deployment summary</span></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>deploy-uat</strong></td>
<td class='td-json'><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Checkout release branch</span> <span class='chip'>Authenticate to UAT sandbox</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy metadata with validation (sf project deploy start --check-only --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Wait for manual approval from Tech Lead</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy to UAT (sf project deploy start --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Run smoke tests</span> <span class='chip'>Notify stakeholders for UAT validation</span></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>deploy-prod</strong></td>
<td class='td-json'><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Checkout main branch</span> <span class='chip'>Authenticate to PROD org</span> <span class='chip'>Run validation deployment (sf project deploy start --check-only --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Wait for manual approval from Product Owner + DevOps Lead</span> <span class='chip'>Create backup of current PROD metadata</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy to PROD (sf project deploy start --test-level RunLocalTests)</span> <span class='chip'>Execute post-deployment validation queries (verify invoice generation, contract status updates)</span> <span class='chip'>Run smoke tests (create test vehicle, rental contract, verify flows execute)</span> <span class='chip'>Tag release in Git (e.g., v1.0.0)</span> <span class='chip'>Create release notes</span> <span class='chip'>Notify all stakeholders</span></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>hotfix-deploy</strong></td>
<td class='td-json'><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Checkout hotfix branch</span> <span class='chip'>Authenticate to PROD</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy with validation</span> <span class='chip'>Emergency approval (single approver)</span> <span class='chip'>Deploy to PROD</span> <span class='chip'>Immediate smoke test</span> <span class='chip'>Merge hotfix back to develop</span> <span class='chip'>Tag hotfix release</span></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='sub-12-5' class='sec-h2'><span>12.5 Rollback Plan</span></h2>
<table class='tbl'>
<thead><tr>
<th>strategy</th>
<th>Metadata revert + data integrity validation</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>steps</td>
<td>• 1. Identify failed components from deployment log (sf project deploy report) <span class='dot'>·</span> 2. Checkout previous stable git tag (e.g., git checkout v1.0.0) <span class='dot'>·</span> 3. Deploy previous version to PROD (sf project deploy start --test-level RunLocalTests) <span class='dot'>·</span> 4. Deactivate any new Flows via Flow metadata (set status to Draft) <span class='dot'>·</span> 5. Deactivate new triggers by deploying with isActive=false <span class='dot'>·</span> 6. Run data integrity validation queries: (a) Verify Vehiclec.Total_Maintenance_Costc matches SUM(Maintenance_Activityc.Costc). (b) Verify Invoice__c records for current month. (c) Check for orphaned records. <span class='dot'>·</span> 7. Restore scheduled jobs to previous configuration <span class='dot'>·</span> 8. Notify stakeholders of rollback with incident report <span class='dot'>·</span> 9. Schedule post-mortem meeting</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>prevention</td>
<td>• Always run --check-only (validation deployment) before actual deploy <span class='dot'>·</span> Require 85%+ Apex test coverage with no test failures <span class='dot'>·</span> Mandatory code review for all Apex changes (2 approvers) <span class='dot'>·</span> Automated PMD static analysis on all PRs <span class='dot'>·</span> UAT sign-off required before PROD deployment <span class='dot'>·</span> Maintain deployment runbook with rollback procedures <span class='dot'>·</span> Schedule PROD deployments during maintenance windows (Saturday 2-6 AM CET)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>data recovery</td>
<td class='td-json'><table class='tbl tbl-kv tbl-nested'><tbody>
<tr><td><span class='key'>backup strategy</span></td><td>Weekly full backup via Salesforce Data Export + daily incremental via Salesforce Backup API</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class='key'>critical objects</span></td><td><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Vehicle__c</span> <span class='chip'>Rental_Contract__c</span> <span class='chip'>Invoice__c</span> <span class='chip'>Maintenance_Activity__c</span> <span class='chip'>Sinistre__c</span></div></td></tr>
<tr><td><span class='key'>recovery time objective</span></td><td>4 hours</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class='key'>recovery point objective</span></td><td>24 hours</td></tr>
</tbody></table></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='sub-12-6' class='sec-h2'><span>12.6 Monitoring</span></h2>
