<td>• Apex test execution: Verify all 12 test classes pass with 85%+ coverage <span class='dot'>·</span> Flow error log: Setup &gt; Process Automation &gt; Paused and Failed Flow Interviews (check for errors in last 24 hours) <span class='dot'>·</span> Login as each profile: (1) LogiFleet_Fleet_Manager, (2) LogiFleet_Driver, (3) LogiFleet_Finance_User - verify access <span class='dot'>·</span> Debug logs: Check for FATAL_ERROR, EXCEPTION entries in last 1 hour <span class='dot'>·</span> Scheduled jobs: Verify all 5 batch jobs are scheduled and next run time is correct <span class='dot'>·</span> Data validation queries: (1) SELECT COUNT() FROM Vehiclec WHERE Total_Maintenance_Costc != (SELECT SUM(Costc) FROM Maintenance_Activityc WHERE Vehiclec = Vehiclec.Id). (2) SELECT COUNT() FROM Invoicec WHERE Billing_Periodc = THIS_MONTH AND Payment_Status__c = 'Unpaid' <span class='dot'>·</span> Mobile app smoke test: Login as driver, submit Problem_Report__c, verify record created</td>
