<tr><td><span class='key'>warning alerts</span></td><td><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Flow interview failure rate &gt;5% in 24 hours</span> <span class='chip'>API usage exceeds 8,000 calls/hour</span> <span class='chip'>Data storage exceeds 80% of limit</span></div></td></tr>
<tr><td><span class='key'>notification channels</span></td><td><div class='chiprow'><span class='chip'>Email: devops@logifleet.com</span> <span class='chip'>Slack: #logifleet-alerts</span> <span class='chip'>PagerDuty: For critical PROD issues</span></div></td></tr>
